@h3 @ul
The @ul tag is used to create an unordered list similar to the *ul* tag
in HTML. Lists can currently be indented 5 levels deep.

@shorte
\@ul
- Item 1
  - Subitem a
    - Sub-subitem y
- Item 2
  - Subitem b

